    "title": "Lead Frontend Developer at Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services",
    "description": "Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Frontend Developer at our Mysuru location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services:\nManipal Digital Health Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Manipal Digital Health Holdings Services!",
